{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "The mission's over. The damage taken was less than expected.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm glad the mission wasn't too hard. It's good to have everyone back safe and sound.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Still, we need to rest up and debrief.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "We can't be slacking on our maintenance. Just like infections in humans, they will grow to be lethal if left untreated for too long.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Lee is always so strict on maintenance.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Not for nothing. I\'m doing this for your "health."', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Especially you, Lucia. You always push yourself too far.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Oh. Sorry about that.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee is so strict!', 3: '21'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'You too, Commandant. You should treat this more seriously as well.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I'm not kidding.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Look what I found! Lee is being a meany to his own commandant!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Fear not, Commandant! I'm here to rescue you!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Welcome back.', 3: '34'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Of course! I did promise you I'd stay safe, didn't I?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Now that I'm here, you can't bully the commandant like that anymore!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: '...Just how dumb are you?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Hey! Why are you always nagging me?!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't want to talk to stupid people.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "And I don't want to talk to you!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'What a friendly banter.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Lee, Kamui, what a great friendship you've got!", 4: '1'}
